{"tid":1398128,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［解鎖任務欄］哨兵請入！手機變對講機","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T18:15:48.000Z","uid":291909,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87a7a839c6b2aa722df5f8e9fda75023421b5397","tid":1398128,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過係發夢現場 消息傳播得又慢又唔update？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後面又唔知前線既行動，又成日叫人退退退<br />\n同朋友吹水之下發現左呢個app   - <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Zello</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 即時對講機！apps版！</strong></span></span><br />\n呢個app 好處在於唔洗用對講機都可以有對講機既效果<br />\n就算你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>關</strong></span>左個mon 都會收到消息，申請既時候又唔需要你既個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要哨兵一講邊到有危險，大家都可以第一時間<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>收到風</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你開擴音又得 帶耳機聽都得 得左！<br />\n根據以往發夢經驗，入夜之後既發夢人數都唔會做到網絡大塞車<br />\n<strong>只需要有個隊長開左個group，share條link出去就加到隊友，到時發夢既時候就知幾時<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沖</span></span>幾時<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留</span></span>幾時<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">守</span></span>，掂呀</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重點！重點！隊長同隊友係唔會show到個人資料！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NCJ2Jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NCJ2Jd.jpg&h=41c07777&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n右下角可以開GP，但係要電話驗證左先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1wnyP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1wnyP5.jpg&h=b1344a79&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n入左gp之後就會見到呢個畫面，按住中間錄音公仔 人地就算聽緊歌定冇開mon，都會播左你講既野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右上角有個關機公仔，用完冇咩事就關左佢，費時夜麻麻有人叫你柯夜尿啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAndroid： <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.loudtalks&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.loudtalks%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDc22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=b6963479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.loudtalks&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\nApple： <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/zello-walkie-talkie/id508231856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fzello-walkie-talkie%2Fid508231856&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDc22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=c3dedbc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/zello-walkie-talkie/id508231856</a>"},{"pid":"f038c24c87dce6b65c27b38d32b9b14a81a4b402","tid":1398128,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5888012e898138805188749dc52129155b38e696","tid":1398128,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98eee8ca7e12de0dd58b9125b0e518847fab4051","tid":1398128,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"8fc35538e298ac03e4948dd19fc6aa5792d7dd1f","tid":1398128,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited